@page
@model AboutModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About VidCore";
}

<div class="about-container">

    <h1>About VidCore</h1>

    <p class="about-subtitle">
        Independent video platform built for creators.
    </p>

    <hr>

    <h2>What is VidCore?</h2>

    <p>
        VidCore is an independent video sharing platform focused on
        creative freedom, open communication, and respect for users.
    </p>

    <p>
        The goal of the project is to provide a simple and enjoyable place
        where people can upload videos, share ideas, and build communities
        without unnecessary complexity.
    </p>

    <h2>Our Philosophy</h2>

    <p>
        We believe that creativity should be accessible to everyone.
    </p>

    <p>
        VidCore supports freedom of expression while maintaining a safe
        environment for users. We encourage creativity, education,
        discussion, entertainment, and innovation.
    </p>

    <p>
        At the same time, content that promotes violence, terrorism,
        harassment, or harm to others has no place on the platform.
    </p>

    <h2>Current Features</h2>

    <ul>
        <li>Video Uploading</li>
        <li>Video Search</li>
        <li>Likes</li>
        <li>Comments</li>
        <li>SQLite Database</li>
        <li>Custom Error Pages</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Developers</h2>

    <div class="developer-card">

        <img src="/spic/mrSashaman.png" class="developer-avatar">

        <h3>mrSashaman</h3>

        <p class="developer-role">
            Founder • Lead Developer • Project Owner
        </p>

    </div>

</div>